^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The bidding was the most interesting part. Although we made 7, actualy I guess six is best with two Kings missing. Next, let's discuss the auction as it went. My 3S is a 2-part bid. Let me briefly discuss a convention called the "Serious 3N", which some experts play. If you play that, and I bid 3N rather than 3S, that says, "Partner we are going to slam if we have controls," you must start bidding controls. 3N forces a control bidding sequence. |
