^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|One other thing to discuss is responses over 5N. There are two ways to respond to 5N. One is called "Specific Kings." That happens to work very well on this hand. 5N asks me if I have any Kings (other than the spade king). If I have a specific King, I am supposed to bid the suit in which I have the King. On this hand, playing specific kings, had I bid 6C showing the Club King, Hope could bid 7. |
